of hearing the news as,

00:15:18.090 --> 00:15:21.050
"An event that I should never
forget, for the rest of my life",

00:15:21.050 --> 00:15:24.200
and after that point he went back
to Frankfurt to continue composing,

00:15:24.200 --> 00:15:27.970
and he took back his position
