00:18:07.650 --> 00:18:08.950
which I just sort of --

00:18:08.950 --> 00:18:13.740
chamber orchestra or large
chamber ensemble size works.

00:18:13.740 --> 00:18:20.450
Which kind of served, I suppose the
more text specific book of works,

00:18:20.450 --> 00:18:22.680
and then his sort of
trying to think of things,

00:18:22.680 --> 00:18:25.600
maybe more in the abstract
or be more objective.

00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:27.380
There's a lot about
Hindemith that's conflicting,

00:18:27.380 --> 00:18:28.690
in terms of what he's trying to do.

00:18:28.690 --> 00:18:31.070
So, at the same time, he had
this really kind of dark,

00:18:31.070 --> 00:18:35.560
