the text of Rocca [phonetic],

00:18:35.560 --> 00:18:37.340
and [inaudible] who we'll get to.

00:18:37.340 --> 00:18:42.890
He's also trying out instrumental
music that doesn't seem necessarily

00:18:42.890 --> 00:18:48.120
to be saying as much, and there
might be reasons for that,

00:18:48.120 --> 00:18:51.360
which we'll get into in a moment.

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:54.120
He also sets interestingly --

00:18:54.120 --> 00:18:56.010
this was the one exception
to this non-cross

00:18:56.010 --> 00:18:58.570
over business between genres.

00:18:58.570 --> 00:19:03.280
So, Whitman poetry throughout his
life, and the revolutionary hymn

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:07.120
which he used, he also
used the same musical theme

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:11.520
from that vocal setting in
