woman becomes completely sucked

00:20:53.030 --> 00:20:57.220
in to the morbidity of
the situation in Germany.

00:20:57.220 --> 00:21:00.610
And the red is representing this
figure that's almost like death,

00:21:00.610 --> 00:21:02.600
the grim reaper coming in the form

00:21:02.600 --> 00:21:07.150
of a little boy, which
is kind of creepy.

00:21:07.150 --> 00:21:10.730
The new objectivity works, are
very much the transition away

00:21:10.730 --> 00:21:13.980
from this expressionist
work that he did.

00:21:13.980 --> 00:21:17.030
So, very much from the string
